<div class="component article-body-text    " data-test="article-body-text">
  
  

	

	
	

	
	



  
  
    <p>Nothing beats real-life browsing in <a class="ck-custom-link" href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/fashion/shopping/15-best-british-boutiques-shop-christmas/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">independent shops</a>, where clothes are treated as treasures to be loved for years, not discarded after a season. Take a very stylish tour around the country’s finest, as nominated by fashion insiders.</p><p><a class="ck-anchor" id="skip-to-region" name="skip-to-region"><em>Skip to region</em></a><em>: </em></p><ul><li><a class="ck-custom-link" href="#south-west">South West</a></li><li><a class="ck-custom-link" href="#south-east">South East</a></li><li><a class="ck-custom-link" href="#south">South</a></li><li><a class="ck-custom-link" href="#london">London</a></li><li><a class="ck-custom-link" href="#the-midlands">The Midlands</a></li><li><a class="ck-custom-link" href="#north-west">North West</a></li><li><a class="ck-custom-link" href="#yorkshire">Yorkshire</a></li><li><a class="ck-custom-link" href="#wales">Wales</a></li><li><a class="ck-custom-link" href="#scotland">Scotland</a></li><li><a class="ck-custom-link" href="#northern-ireland">Northern Ireland</a></li></ul><h2 class="u-heading-size-large u-heading-style-normal"><a class="ck-anchor" id="south-west" name="south-west">South West</a></h2><h2 class="u-heading-size-medium u-heading-style-normal">The Yellow Shop</h2><p>‘Any time a friend mentions they’re visiting Bath, I always recommend popping into this iconic pre-loved institution that peddles a fantastic variety of secondhand garments, from vintage leather jackets and funky sunglasses, to distressed denim and great shirts. Always worth a rummage.’ Sophie Saint, digital creator and second-hand fashion advocate.</p>
  
</div>
</div>
