<div class="articleBodyText section">




<div class="component article-body-text    " data-test="article-body-text">
  
  

	

	
	

	
	



  
  
    <p><em>72 Walcot Street, Bath BA1, </em><a class="ck-custom-link" href="https://www.theyellowshop.co.uk/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><em>theyellowshop.co.uk</em></a></p><h2 class="u-heading-size-medium u-heading-style-normal">Sumptuous Designerwear</h2><p>‘Perfect for <a class="ck-custom-link" href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/fashion/style/buying-pre-loved-has-never-been-easier-more-inspiring/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">secondhand designer pieces</a>, with everything from suits and sets to shoes and bags. Think Chanel, Dior and Coach, as well as handmade pieces and elevated high-street brands like Russell &amp; Bromley,’ says Izzy Manuel, sustainable fashion and lifestyle creator.</p><p><em>68 Walcot Street, Bath BA1, </em><a class="ck-custom-link" href="https://www.instagram.com/sumptuous_designerwear/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><em>&#64;sumptuous_designwear</em></a><em> </em></p><h2 class="u-heading-size-medium u-heading-style-normal">Fox &#43; Feather</h2><p>Founder Clare prides herself on offering cool, indie brands at high-street prices. Stocking the likes of Sugarhill Brighton, Ichi and Frnch, as well as its own Fox &#43; Feather label, it’s brimming with bold colours and bright prints.</p>
  
