    <p><em>20A High Street, Deal CT14, </em><a class="ck-custom-link" href="https://positive-retail.com/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><em>positive-retail.com</em></a><em>. Branches also at: 1 Broad Street, Margate CT9; 5 Kings Road, St Leonards TN37</em></p><h2 class="u-heading-size-medium u-heading-style-normal">Atwin Store</h2><p>Named after the old Norfolk dialect for ‘between’, Atwin has a strong sense of community. It’s  run by lifelong friends Bonnie, of jewellery label Studio Adorn, and Sarah, of clothing brand Harwood, and stocks some of the finest makers in Norfolk and the UK.</p>
  
